<br>
Non-Medical Euthanasia:<br>
<br>
As far as I know, suicide isn't illegal. We as a society try and prevent it, but we don't throw people in jail over it. I am pretty much of the same opinion with this as I am the medical version. An adult, of sane mind, should have the right to choose to end his/her life in a peaceful manner. It's theirs. They are the ones who have to live it, not me or you or any other law-making body.<br>
<br>
<br>
nuff said. <p>Mistress Lorelai Darkensoul<br>
